OL,12,FIndustrial Strategy Committee said the 
OL,13,Fgovernment's approach to decarbonising 
OL,14,Fhome heating lacked clear direction.   
OL,16,FCurrent policies are also not on the   
OL,17,Fscale required, they said.             
OL,19,FHowever, the report rejected hydrogen  
OL,20,Fas a solution for greener home heating.
